snippet: The couple are to be married on Long Island
lead_paragraph: Daniel Joseph Fischer and Stephan Michael Mandresh are to be married Sunday at the Jamesport Manor Inn in Jamesport, N.Y. The Rev. Debra A. Viola, who is affiliated with the Sanctuary of Peace & Harmony, an interfaith seminary in Huntington Station, N.Y., is to officiate. Mr. Fischer, 55, is a senior pharmacist at Stony Brook University Hospital in Stony Brook, N.Y. He graduated from St. John's University and received a master's in pastoral theology from Immaculate Conception Seminary in Huntington, N.Y. Mr. Fischer's previous marriage ended in divorce.
